{"id":533688,"date":[{"year":1974,"month":1,"day":23}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"沿着毛主席的无产阶级文艺路线胜利前进(全国摄影艺术展览作品选)","genre":"","count":"132","ytitle":"","mtitle":"关怀","ftitle":"","authors":["王鲁夫"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"王鲁夫　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿柳下，飞针走线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑盈盈，把衣角缝补；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无取胜的阶级情感呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在向新鲜血液里倾注!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道是普通的缝补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这却是延安精神的一课。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中盛满老贫农的爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一肩能挑起大山一座。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入6号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1974\\01\\741n050401.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>汪阳春</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>汪阳春　摄影　</FONT>"}]}